For the next run, it is recommended to address the unexpected weight loading issues by ensuring compatibility between the pre-trained model and the downstream task. Also, initializing or fine-tuning the missing parameters could improve model performance. Furthermore, optimizing the data loader configuration to handle 'pin_memory' appropriately on the MPS device would enhance memory efficiency during training.